msgid "0:岸本あやせは、ベッドの上でぼんやりと窓の外を眺めている。[%p]"
msgstr "0:Ayase Kishimoto was staring out the window, only half paying attention to anything going on around her.[%p]"

msgid "100:この病室の窓には、あやせが昔いたアークハートメディカル会のような鉄格子はなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "100:There were no bars on the windows like there were in the rooms at Ark Heart Medical, the place she'd been before.[%p]"

msgid "200:窓の外には新宿の高層ビル群、そして夕焼け空が広がっている。ハトが数羽、翼を激しく羽ばたかせて横切っていった。[%p]"
msgstr "200:Outside, she could see the high-rise buildings of Shinjuku, and beyond them, a blazing evening sky. A few pigeons were flapping furiously across it.[%p]"

msgid "300:あやせはときおり苦しそうに眉根を寄せる。[%p]"
msgstr "300:Occasionally, she would wince in pain.[%p]"

msgid "400:その瞳はわずかに眠たげで、なにも映しておらず。[linebreak]その唇が、渋谷の若者を魅了したあの美声を口ずさむこともない。[%p]"
msgstr "400:Her eyes were empty, and just a little tired. She wasn't humming the songs that had so entranced the young people of Shibuya.[%p]"

msgid "500:自殺未遂騒動を起こしたあやせが収容されたのは、代々木にある大きな総合病院の精神科だった。[%p]"
msgstr "500:After her failed suicide attempt, she'd been brought to a big general hospital in Yoyogi.[%p]"

msgid "600:すでにケガはほとんど治っていた。[%p]"
msgstr "600:Her wounds had almost completely healed.[%p]"

msgid "700:あの高さから落ちたにもかかわらず、ほんのかすり傷程度で済んだのは奇跡的なことだと医師は言った。[%p]"
msgstr "700:The doctors had said it was a miracle that a fall from that height had ended in only a few minor scrapes and bruises.[%p]"

msgid "800:それでも、頭を強く打ったこともあり、様子を見るためにすでに一週間以上、ここに入院させられている。[%p]"
msgstr "800:Still, she'd hit her head hard, so she'd been hospitalized for observation. She'd been here over a week already.[%p]"

msgid "900:もっとも、様子を見ると言っても２日に一度ほどの割合で簡単な検査をするだけで、後は基本的にほったらかしだった。[%p]"
msgstr "900:Of course, “observation” meant nothing more than a simple checkup once every two days. The rest of the time, she was left to herself.[%p]"

msgid "1000:病室は個室で、他にベッドはない。[%p]"
msgstr "1000:She had the room to herself. There were no other beds in it.[%p]"

msgid "1100:窓際には、彼女のディソードが立て掛けてあった。青い光を明滅させている。それはもうずっとそこに置いてあるが、この病室を訪れた人間で気付いた者はひとりもいない。[%p]"
msgstr "1100:Her Di-Sword was up against the window, flashing with a pale light. It'd been there the whole time she'd been here, but nobody had noticed it.[%p]"

msgid "1200:見舞客はあまり来ない。[%p]"
msgstr "1200:She didn't get many visitors.[%p]"

msgid "1300:ファンタズムのファンたちは、毎日のように押し寄せているらしいが、周囲の迷惑になるからという理由で病院が面会を禁止していた。[%p]"
msgstr "1300:Phantasm fans were, supposedly, coming in huge numbers every day. But the hospital had banned them from seeing her, so they wouldn't bother the other patients.[%p]"

msgid "1400:家族とは疎遠になっているあやせには、他に見舞いに来る人間はほとんどいない。[%p]"
msgstr "1400:She and her family weren't close. Almost nobody else came to see her.[%p]"

msgid "1500:バンドの仲間は一度顔を出したが、そのときにあやせの口からバンド解散の話が出て、それ以来ぱったりと連絡が付かなくなった。[%p]"
msgstr "1500:Her bandmates had come to see her once. When she'd mentioned breaking up the band, though, they'd stopped coming at all.[%p]"

msgid "1600:[name]看護師[line]「岸本さーん、体温計、ピピッて鳴りました？」[%p]"
msgstr "1600:[name]看護師[line]Kishimoto, did your thermometer go beep?[%p]"

msgid "1700:病室のドアが開いて、白衣を着た看護師が入ってくる。[%p]"
msgstr "1700:The door opened and a nurse in white came in.[%p]"

msgid "1800:あやせは彼女の方にのろのろと顔を向け、それから今この瞬間に思い出したかのように、腋に挟んでいた体温計を抜き取った。[%p]"
msgstr "1800:Ayase slowly turned toward her, and then took the thermometer out from under her arm like she'd just remembered it was there.[%p]"

msgid "1900:看護師はそこに表示されたデジタルの数字を見て、持っていたボードに書き込む。[%p]"
msgstr "1900:The nurse looked at the number on the digital display and wrote it down on the chart.[%p]"

msgid "2000:[name]看護師[line]「３７度１分、と……」[%p]"
msgstr "2000:[name]看護師[line]37.1 degrees Celsius.[%p]"

msgid "2100:[name]看護師[line]「ちょっと熱っぽいかしら」[%p]"
msgstr "2100:[name]看護師[line]You've got a little fever, maybe.[%p]"

msgid "2200:[name]あやせ[line]「ズキズキするわ……頭」[%p]"
msgstr "2200:[name]あやせ[line]My head... hurts.[%p]"

msgid "2300:あやせはまた苦しそうに顔をしかめた。[%p]"
msgstr "2300:Ayase winced in pain again.[%p]"

msgid "2400:[name]看護師[line]「あら、また頭痛？」[%p]"
msgstr "2400:[name]看護師[line]Oh my. Another headache?[%p]"

msgid "2500:[name]看護師[line]「でもそれは薬の副作用よ。気にしなくてもそのうちよくなりますよ」[%p]"
msgstr "2500:[name]看護師[line]It's a side effect of the medicine, though. It'll eventually go away.[%p]"

msgid "2600:あやせから体温計を返してもらった看護師が、笑顔でそう答える。[linebreak]その表情は柔らかで、患者を安心させる優しさがある。[%p]"
msgstr "2600:The nurse spoke with a smile and took the thermometer. Her expression was gentle, and there was something about her that put a patient at ease.[%p]"

msgid "2700:だがあやせは、手で額を押さえて首を振った。[%p]"
msgstr "2700:But Ayase put her hand to her forehead and shook her head.[%p]"

msgid "2800:入院して以来、あやせはずっと鈍い頭痛に悩まされている。[linebreak]痛い、というほどのものではなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "2800:Ever since she came here, Ayase had been dealing with a dull headache. “Painful” wasn't the word for it.[%p]"

msgid "2900:だが、頭の中で脳が脈動しているかのような不快な感覚が常にあって、それがあやせの思考能力を鈍麻させている。[%p]"
msgstr "2900:But there was an unpleasant sensation of something pulsing in her head. It was making it hard for her to think.[%p]"

msgid "3000:それに、身体も鉛のように重い。[%p]"
msgstr "3000:And her whole body felt as heavy as lead.[%p]"

msgid "3100:あやせには、こんな症状になったことが過去にもあった。[linebreak]アークハートメディカル会にいた頃だ。[%p]"
msgstr "3100:This had happened to Ayase before, too. It was when she was at Ark Heart Medical.[%p]"

msgid "3200:あの頃は頭痛に２４時間３６５日蝕まれ、まともに眠ることもできず、感情が不安定になっていた。[%p]"
msgstr "3200:The headaches had lasted 24 hours a day, 365 days a year. She'd been unable to sleep, and emotionally unstable.[%p]"

msgid "3300:思い出したくない思い出。[linebreak]封印した過去。[linebreak]２年ほど前の記憶。[%p]"
msgstr "3300:It was a past she didn't want to remember. A past she'd sealed away. Her memories of two years ago...[%p]"

msgid "3400:頭の痛みを引き金にして、脳裏にフラッシュバックする。[%p]"
msgstr "3400:The pain was the trigger that made them come flashing back.[%p]"

msgid "3500:暗い部屋。[linebreak]鉄格子がはめられた小さな窓。[%p]"
msgstr "3500:A dark room. A small window with bars.[%p]"

msgid "3600:その窓以外の壁全面には、鏡が張られている。[linebreak]あやせは部屋の真ん中に固定された、鋼鉄製の無骨なイスに座らされている。[%p]"
msgstr "3600:Except for the small window, the walls were entirely covered with mirrors. She'd been restrained in a steel chair in the center of the room.[%p]"

msgid "3700:頭には、たくさんのコードがついたヘッドギアのようなものを被らされ、[%p]"
msgstr "3700:There was some kind of device on her head, with cords stretching off of it.[%p]"

msgid "3800:手は背もたれに回すようにして後ろ手に縛られ、[%p]"
msgstr "3800:Her hands were bound behind the chair's back.[%p]"

msgid "3900:顔はわずかに顎をそらすような向きで固定されている。[%p]"
msgstr "3900:Her head was restrained at a slight angle.[%p]"

msgid "4000:部屋の中に他に人影はなく。[%p]"
msgstr "4000:There was no one else in the room.[%p]"

msgid "4100:あやせの荒い息づかいと、イスが軋む音だけが響き続けていた。[%p]"
msgstr "4100:The only sounds were her panting for air, and the straining of the metal chair.[%p]"

msgid "4200:[name]あやせ[line]「ああ……ああああああ」[%p]"
msgstr "4200:[name]あやせ[line]Aaah! Aaaah![%p]"

msgid "4300:あやせは口の端からよだれを垂らし、まだ年端もいかぬ少女のものとは思えない、獣のようなうめき声をあげていた。[%p]"
msgstr "4300:Drool was flying from her lips, and a bestial howl was coming from her throat that one would've thought impossible for a girl her age.[%p]"

msgid "4400:[name]あやせ[line]「殺して――」[%p]"
msgstr "4400:[name]あやせ[line]Kill me![%p]"

msgid "4500:[name]あやせ[line]「殺してぇぇぇっ」[%p]"
msgstr "4500:[name]あやせ[line]KILL ME![%p]"

msgid "4600:それは、とても、静かな、拷問だった。[%p]"
msgstr "4600:It was a very quiet form of torture.[%p]"

msgid "4700:されていることはたったひとつ。[%p]"
msgstr "4700:There was only one thing they were doing to her.[%p]"

msgid "4800:彼女の額に、上から、正確に、狂いなく、５秒ほどの間隔で、水滴が落ちてくる。[%p]"
msgstr "4800:A single drop of water was falling on her forehead from above, in the same spot every time, at precise five-second intervals.[%p]"

msgid "4900:ただ、それだけ。[%p]"
msgstr "4900:That was all.[%p]"

msgid "5000:その状態が、２日ほど休みなく続けられた結果、[%p]"
msgstr "5000:She'd been stuck like that for two days with no rest.[%p]"

msgid "5100:あやせは“次に落ちてくる水滴”のことしか考えられなくなり、[%p]"
msgstr "5100:And now all she could think of was when the next drop would fall.[%p]"

msgid "5200:感覚は極限にまで研ぎ澄まされ、[%p]"
msgstr "5200:Her senses were pushed to their limits.[%p]"

msgid "5300:その水滴が額に当たるたびに、[%p]"
msgstr "5300:Each time a drop fell,[%p]"

msgid "5400:全身の神経を引きちぎられるような錯覚、[%p]"
msgstr "5400:it felt like all the nerves in her body were being ripped apart.[%p]"

msgid "5500:全身の骨が粉々に砕かれるかのような錯覚、[%p]"
msgstr "5500:Like all the bones in her body were being shattered to pieces.[%p]"

msgid "5600:長く鋭利な千枚通しで頭を貫かれたような錯覚、[%p]"
msgstr "5600:Like a long sharp awl was being driven into her skull.[%p]"

msgid "5700:血も含めた体内のあらゆる水分が凍り付くような錯覚、[%p]"
msgstr "5700:Like all the fluids in her body, including her blood, were freezing.[%p]"

msgid "5800:全身の皮膚がぐずぐずに腐ってずる剥けるような錯覚、[%p]"
msgstr "5800:Like all her skin was rotting and sloughing off.[%p]"

msgid "5900:それらに襲われ、まともな精神ではいられなくなった。[%p]"
msgstr "5900:It was more than enough to drive her mad.[%p]"

msgid "6000:[name]あやせ[line]「っ……はあっ……は……あ……」[%p]"
msgstr "6000:[name]あやせ[line]Hahh... Hahh...[%p]"

msgid "6100:我に返り、荒い呼吸を繰り返しながらシーツをきつく握りしめる。[linebreak]暗い記憶がよみがえってしまったことに、彼女は身を震わせる。[%p]"
msgstr "6100:She snapped back to reality to find herself panting and clutching the sheets tightly. Her whole body had started to shake when her dark memories came back.[%p]"

msgid "6200:病室に、先ほどの看護師の姿はすでにない。[linebreak]ちょうど夕食時で、廊下の外はバタバタとしていた。[%p]"
msgstr "6200:The nurse was gone from her room. It was dinnertime, and there was a frantic rush of movement outside the doors.[%p]"

msgid "6300:あやせはさっきの看護師の言葉を心の中で反すうする。[%p]"
msgstr "6300:Ayase repeated the words that the nurse had said to herself.[%p]"

msgid "6400:この頭痛が本当に薬の副作用なのか、[linebreak]あるいは自分が飛び降りたときに頭を打ったせいなのか、[linebreak]過去の記憶の影響による錯覚なのか、それは分からなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "6400:Was this headache really caused by the medicine? Or had she hit her head when she'd fallen? Or was it an effect of her old memories? She couldn't tell.[%p]"

msgid "6500:[name]あやせ[line]「ふ、ふふ……」[%p]"
msgstr "6500:[name]あやせ[line]Heh... Heheh...[%p]"

msgid "6600:額ににじむ汗を拭い、あやせは自嘲気味な笑みを浮かべる。[%p]"
msgstr "6600:Ayase wiped away the sweat on her forehead and began to laugh.[%p]"

msgid "6700:[name]あやせ[line]「構わないわ……今さら、なにをされたって……」[%p]"
msgstr "6700:[name]あやせ[line]I don't care... I don't care what you do to me now.[%p]"

msgid "6800:[name]あやせ[line]「あれを、あの神罰を、耐え抜いたんだから……」[%p]"
msgstr "6800:[name]あやせ[line]I survived the divine punishment.[%p]"

msgid "6900:[name]あやせ[line]「もう、迷わない、私は」[%p]"
msgstr "6900:[name]あやせ[line]I know exactly what I have to do.[%p]"

msgid "7000:浮かされたようにつぶやいてから、あやせはふと、廊下から響く音に気付く。[%p]"
msgstr "7000:She whispered, as if in a trance. Then, suddenly, she heard a sound coming from the hallway.[%p]"

msgid "7100:心地よささえ感じさせる、リノリウムを蹴る靴の音。[%p]"
msgstr "7100:It was the pleasant sound of shoes on linoleum.[%p]"

msgid "7200:看護師のものではなかった。[linebreak]靴音は、あやせがいる病室へと大股で近づいてくる。[%p]"
msgstr "7200:They weren't the nurse's footsteps. She could tell that much. The footsteps were getting closer to her room.[%p]"

msgid "7300:ドアがノックされ、あやせは唇を引き結んだ。[%p]"
msgstr "7300:There was a knock at the door. She pressed her lips together tightly in a frown.[%p]"

msgid "7400:[name]？？？[line]「失礼しまッス」[%p]"
msgstr "7400:[name]？？？[line]Hello there![%p]"

msgid "7500:現れたのは、ひとりの男。その手には、たくさんのフルーツが入ったお見舞い用のバスケット。[%p]"
msgstr "7500:It was a man. He was holding a fruit basket, the type commonly given as a gift.[%p]"

msgid "7600:[name]あやせ[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "7600:[name]あやせ[line]...[%p]"

msgid "7700:あやせはこの男に見覚えがある。故に、警戒の目で男を見つめた。[%p]"
msgstr "7700:Ayase recognized the man. Thus, she looked at him suspiciously.[%p]"

msgid "7800:[name]男[line]「どうも。あ、別に怪しいもんじゃないッスよ？\u3000自分は――」[%p]"
msgstr "7800:[name]男[line]Hey there. Oh, don't worry. I'm not here to hurt you. I'm...[%p]"

msgid "7900:[name]あやせ[line]「知ってるわ」[%p]"
msgstr "7900:[name]あやせ[line]I know.[%p]"

msgid "8000:この男は警視庁の刑事。[linebreak]かつてあやせを、ニュージェネ事件の重要参考人としてつけ回してきたことがある。[%p]"
msgstr "8000:He was a detective from the Tokyo Metropolitan Police. He'd once been tailing her as a person of interest in the NewGen case.[%p]"

msgid "8100:刑事は嬉しそうに頭を掻いている。[linebreak]ずいぶんと呑気な態度だった。[%p]"
msgstr "8100:He scratched his head happily. For a detective, he seemed surprisingly laid back.[%p]"

msgid "8200:[name]青年刑事[line]「いやー、嬉しいッス。キミみたいな美人に覚えててもらえて」[%p]"
msgstr "8200:[name]青年刑事[line]Aw, that makes me happy. To have a pretty girl like you remember me, I mean.[%p]"

msgid "8300:[name]青年刑事[line]「記憶力、いいんスね」[%p]"
msgstr "8300:[name]青年刑事[line]You've got a good memory.[%p]"

msgid "8400:[name]あやせ[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "8400:[name]あやせ[line]...[%p]"

msgid "8500:刑事はベッドに歩み寄った。[%p]"
msgstr "8500:The detective walked toward her bed.[%p]"

msgid "8600:あやせはチラリと、窓際に立て掛けられたディソードへと目をやる。[linebreak]手を伸ばしただけでは届かない位置に、それはある。[%p]"
msgstr "8600:Ayase glanced at the Di-Sword on the windowsill. It was too far away for her to reach out and grab.[%p]"

msgid "8700:[name]青年刑事[line]「今日はお見舞いに来たんスよ」[%p]"
msgstr "8700:[name]青年刑事[line]I was thinking you might want some company, so I brought you this fruit basket.[%p]"

msgid "8800:[name]あやせ[line]「……そうは思えないわ」[%p]"
msgstr "8800:[name]あやせ[line]I don't think that's true.[%p]"

msgid "8900:[name]あやせ[line]「目的は？」[%p]"
msgstr "8900:[name]あやせ[line]What do you want?[%p]"

msgid "9000:[name]青年刑事[line]「す、鋭いッスね」[%p]"
msgstr "9000:[name]青年刑事[line]Y-You're pretty sharp, huh?[%p]"

msgid "9100:刑事はあからさまにたじろいで見せた。[linebreak]どこか芝居がかったような態度。[%p]"
msgstr "9100:The detective acted like he was shaken. But it felt a little like an act.[%p]"

msgid "9200:[name]青年刑事[line]「まあ、ちょっとあやせちゃんに聞きたいことがあって」[%p]"
msgstr "9200:[name]青年刑事[line]Well... I guess there's something I want to ask you.[%p]"

msgid "9300:[name]あやせ[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "9300:[name]あやせ[line]...[%p]"

msgid "9400:[name]青年刑事[line]「あ、これ、よかったら食べてほしいッス」[%p]"
msgstr "9400:[name]青年刑事[line]Oh, here. This is for you.[%p]"

msgid "9500:無邪気な笑顔で、刑事は持っていたバスケットを差し出し、半ば一方的にあやせの足許に置いた。[%p]"
msgstr "9500:He offered her the fruit basket with an innocent smile, practically forcing her to take it by placing it at the foot of her bed.[%p]"

msgid "9600:[name]青年刑事[line]「うまいッスよ。あと……高かった……トホホ」[%p]"
msgstr "9600:[name]青年刑事[line]It's really good fruit! Also, it was... really expensive. Sob.[%p]"

msgid "9700:[name]あやせ[line]「……いらない」[%p]"
msgstr "9700:[name]あやせ[line]No thanks.[%p]"

msgid "9800:[name]青年刑事[line]「まあそう言わず。せっかく買ってきたんで」[%p]"
msgstr "9800:[name]青年刑事[line]Come on, don't say that. I already spent the money on it.[%p]"

msgid "9900:[name]青年刑事[line]「後でお母さんが来たときにでも、切ってもらって」[%p]"
msgstr "9900:[name]青年刑事[line]When your mom comes later you can share it with her or something.[%p]"

msgid "10000:[name]あやせ[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "10000:[name]あやせ[line]...[%p]"

msgid "10100:[name]青年刑事[line]「あ、し、しまった。あやせちゃんは、もう何年も両親に会ってないんだったッスね……」[%p]"
msgstr "10100:[name]青年刑事[line]Oh, w-whoops. You haven't seen your parents for years, have you?[%p]"

msgid "10200:刑事の白々しい態度にも、あやせは特になにも感じない。[%p]"
msgstr "10200:It was clear the detective knew exactly what he was doing, but Ayase didn't really care.[%p]"

msgid "10300:幼い頃に、彼女は親から縁を切られた。[%p]"
msgstr "10300:Her parents had disowned her when she was very little.[%p]"

msgid "10400:両親は体面を気にする人間で、当時問題ばかり起こしていたあやせの存在は彼らにとって都合が悪かったのだ。[%p]"
msgstr "10400:They were the type to really care what the neighbors thought of them, and Ayase was a problem child that they were eager to be rid of.[%p]"

msgid "10500:一応、まだ繋がりはある。生活費だけは毎月、口座に振り込まれてくるのだ。[%p]"
msgstr "10500:She wasn't entirely cut off from them, though. They sent her enough money to pay her living expenses every month.[%p]"

msgid "10600:[name]青年刑事[line]「申し訳ないッス」[%p]"
msgstr "10600:[name]青年刑事[line]Sorry.[%p]"

msgid "10700:刑事はペコリと頭を下げた。[%p]"
msgstr "10700:He gave her a little bob of his head in apology.[%p]"

msgid "10800:あやせは先ほどのフラッシュバックによる動揺がようやくおさまりつつあったものの、あまりこの刑事と話したくないと思い、自分から話を促した。[%p]"
msgstr "10800:Ayase was only now starting to recover from her flashback earlier, and didn't really want to talk to the detective at all. She decided to get this over with as fast as possible.[%p]"

msgid "10900:[name]あやせ[line]「聞きたいことって、なに？」[%p]"
msgstr "10900:[name]あやせ[line]What did you want to ask me about?[%p]"

msgid "11000:[name]あやせ[line]「アリバイ？」[%p]"
msgstr "11000:[name]あやせ[line]My alibi?[%p]"

msgid "11100:[name]青年刑事[line]「違うッスよ。それは前に散々聞いたし」[%p]"
msgstr "11100:[name]青年刑事[line]Nah. We already talked to you about that more than enough.[%p]"

msgid "11200:[name]青年刑事[line]「もうあやせちゃんの容疑は晴れたッス。キミは白。真っ白」[%p]"
msgstr "11200:[name]青年刑事[line]You're not under suspicion anymore. You're innocent. Completely innocent.[%p]"

msgid "11300:[name]あやせ[line]「目星は付いたの？」[%p]"
msgstr "11300:[name]あやせ[line]Do you have a suspect, then?[%p]"

msgid "11400:[name]あやせ[line]「――犯人の」[%p]"
msgstr "11400:[name]あやせ[line]For the murders.[%p]"

msgid "11500:[name]青年刑事[line]「それは教えられないんスよ。捜査上の秘密ッス」[%p]"
msgstr "11500:[name]青年刑事[line]I can't tell you that. Classified information, you see.[%p]"

msgid "11600:[name]あやせ[line]「……拓巳？」[%p]"
msgstr "11600:[name]あやせ[line]Takumi?[%p]"

msgid "11700:[name]青年刑事[line]「秘密ッス」[%p]"
msgstr "11700:[name]青年刑事[line]It's a secret.[%p]"

msgid "11800:刑事はニコニコとしている。[linebreak]笑ってごまかしているのだった。[%p]"
msgstr "11800:The detective was grinning. He was clearly hiding something.[%p]"

msgid "11900:そうやって笑うと、まだ垢抜けていない部分が垣間見えてくる。[%p]"
msgstr "11900:When he laughed, you could see just how young he still was.[%p]"

msgid "12000:[name]青年刑事[line]「しかし西條くんは、不思議な少年ッスねえ」[%p]"
msgstr "12000:[name]青年刑事[line]Nishijo's certainly a strange boy, though.[%p]"

msgid "12100:[name]青年刑事[line]「彼を見ていると、殺人の容疑者にはとても見えない」[%p]"
msgstr "12100:[name]青年刑事[line]He doesn't look like a murderer at all, you know.[%p]"

msgid "12200:[name]青年刑事[line]「もしあれで本当に犯人だったとしたら……[linebreak]まさに人の皮をかぶった悪魔ッス！」[%p]"
msgstr "12200:[name]青年刑事[line]If he really is the killer... Then he's a demon wearing human skin![%p]"

msgid "12300:[name]あやせ[line]「まだ容疑者なのね、彼」[%p]"
msgstr "12300:[name]あやせ[line]He's still a suspect, isn't he?[%p]"

msgid "12400:[name]青年刑事[line]「いや、そういうわけじゃないッスよ？」[%p]"
msgstr "12400:[name]青年刑事[line]No, that's actually not true.[%p]"

msgid "12500:あやせがしつこく指摘しても、刑事は笑いながらあっさり否定した。[%p]"
msgstr "12500:The detective laughed and shook his head.[%p]"

msgid "12600:[name]青年刑事[line]「あ、今の話、誰にも言っちゃダメッスからね」[%p]"
msgstr "12600:[name]青年刑事[line]Oh, don't tell anyone I said that.[%p]"

msgid "12700:[name]あやせ[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "12700:[name]あやせ[line]...[%p]"

msgid "12800:[name]青年刑事[line]「情報漏洩すると、上司に怒られるんスよ。まあ当然なんスけど」[%p]"
msgstr "12800:[name]青年刑事[line]My bosses get mad when I leak information. I mean, of course they do.[%p]"

msgid "12900:[name]青年刑事[line]「この前も先輩のとばっちりで怒られたばっかで」[%p]"
msgstr "12900:[name]青年刑事[line]My partner screwed up just the other day, and I got yelled at for it.[%p]"

msgid "13000:[name]青年刑事[line]「あやせちゃんも一度会ってると思うんスけど、覚えてるかなあ」[%p]"
msgstr "13000:[name]青年刑事[line]I think you've met him, Ayase. Do you remember?[%p]"

msgid "13100:[name]青年刑事[line]「判さんっていう、髪がぼさぼさで無精ヒゲ生やしたおっさん刑事」[%p]"
msgstr "13100:[name]青年刑事[line]His name's Ban. Older guy, messy hair. Stubble.[%p]"

msgid "13200:あやせは覚えていた。[%p]"
msgstr "13200:Ayase remembered him.[%p]"

msgid "13300:話を聞かれたときも、今ここにいる若い刑事より、むしろそのおじさん刑事の方が口数は多かった。[%p]"
msgstr "13300:When they'd come to talk to her, it was the older man, not the one in front of her, who'd done most of the speaking.[%p]"

msgid "13400:そしてその話し方はかなりねちっこかった。[%p]"
msgstr "13400:He'd been pretty aggressive and sneaky, too.[%p]"

msgid "13500:[name]青年刑事[line]「あの人がすぐ、“このバカ”って怒鳴るんスよ」[%p]"
msgstr "13500:[name]青年刑事[line]He always yells at me, you know. Calls me an idiot.[%p]"

msgid "13600:[name]青年刑事[line]「そのくせ自分は本来の捜査をせずに、なんだか訳の分からないことばっか調べてて」[%p]"
msgstr "13600:[name]青年刑事[line]But what does he do? He ignores his job and goes off to look into weird stuff.[%p]"

msgid "13700:[name]青年刑事[line]「挙げ句の果てに自分まで無理矢理付き合わされて……」[%p]"
msgstr "13700:[name]青年刑事[line]And then he forces me to come with him.[%p]"

msgid "13800:[name]青年刑事[line]「最近、胃が痛いんスよね〜」[%p]"
msgstr "13800:[name]青年刑事[line]Lately, I've been getting the worst stomachaches.[%p]"

msgid "13900:[name]青年刑事[line]「いや、まあ、根はいい人ッスし、勘が異常に鋭い人で、過去にも難事件をいくつか解決に導いたらしいんスけどね……」[%p]"
msgstr "13900:[name]青年刑事[line]I mean, he's a good guy at heart. And he's really smart. Supposedly he's solved a bunch of really tough cases. But you know...[%p]"

msgid "14000:[name]あやせ[line]「その話をするため？」[%p]"
msgstr "14000:[name]あやせ[line]Is that why you came here?[%p]"

msgid "14100:[name]あやせ[line]「ここに来たのは」[%p]"
msgstr "14100:[name]あやせ[line]To complain about your partner?[%p]"

msgid "14200:あやせに話を遮えぎられ、刑事は苦笑した。[%p]"
msgstr "14200:The detective chuckled when Ayase cut him off.[%p]"

msgid "14300:[name]青年刑事[line]「あ、いや。申し訳ないッス。つい愚痴入っちゃったッスね」[%p]"
msgstr "14300:[name]青年刑事[line]Oh, sorry. Sorry. I lost control of myself for a moment.[%p]"

msgid "14400:[name]青年刑事[line]「今の話は全面的に内緒にしてほしいッス。諏訪護、一生のお願いッスよ！」[%p]"
msgstr "14400:[name]青年刑事[line]Please, don't tell anybody what I said! I, Mamoru Suwa, am begging you![%p]"

msgid "14500:[name]あやせ[line]「それで？」[%p]"
msgstr "14500:[name]あやせ[line]So?[%p]"

msgid "14600:[name]青年刑事[line]「えーっと、ひとつめは」[%p]"
msgstr "14600:[name]青年刑事[line]Um... first question.[%p]"

msgid "14700:[name]青年刑事[line]「なんで、あんなことを？」[%p]"
msgstr "14700:[name]青年刑事[line]Why did you do it?[%p]"

msgid "14800:それが、学校の屋上から飛び降りたことを指しているのは、あやせにも分かった。[%p]"
msgstr "14800:Even Ayase could tell he was talking about how she'd jumped off the roof.[%p]"

msgid "14900:[name]あやせ[line]「もう何度も話したわ。他の、刑事さんに」[%p]"
msgstr "14900:[name]あやせ[line]I've already told this story many times. To the other detectives.[%p]"

msgid "15000:[name]青年刑事[line]「邪心王グラジオールの復活を阻止するため、ッスか？」[%p]"
msgstr "15000:[name]青年刑事[line]To stop Gladiale, the King of Wicked Hearts, from reviving? Was that it?[%p]"

msgid "15100:[name]あやせ[line]「死ぬつもりなんてなかった」[%p]"
msgstr "15100:[name]あやせ[line]It wasn't a suicide attempt.[%p]"

msgid "15200:[name]あやせ[line]「魂を、ひとつ上のステージに持っていこうとしただけよ」[%p]"
msgstr "15200:[name]あやせ[line]I was trying to bring my soul to a higher plane. That's all.[%p]"

msgid "15300:[name]青年刑事[line]「例の、若者の間で話題になったキミの歌についても、似たようなこと言ってたッスよね？」[%p]"
msgstr "15300:[name]青年刑事[line]You were saying something similar about that song of yours. The one all the kids are listening to.[%p]"

msgid "15400:それが２個目の質問だった。[linebreak]あやせは小さく息をつく。[%p]"
msgstr "15400:That was his second question. Ayase couldn't help but sigh a little.[%p]"

msgid "15500:[name]あやせ[line]「ニュージェネのことを歌ったものなんかじゃないわ、あの詞は」[%p]"
msgstr "15500:[name]あやせ[line]That song's not about NewGen.[%p]"

msgid "15600:[name]あやせ[line]「[color index="A0FF0000"]グラジオール記黙示録詩編[color index="800000"]のインスピレーションを受けて作った。第３章１０２節よ」[%p]"
msgstr "15600:[name]あやせ[line]It was inspired by [color index="A0FF0000"]the Apocalyptic Psalms of the Book of Gladiale[color index="800000"]. Chapter 3, Verse 102.[%p]"

msgid "15700:[name]あやせ[line]「世界に、邪心王グラジオールが現れようとしている」[%p]"
msgstr "15700:[name]あやせ[line]Gladiale, the King of Wicked Hearts, is about to descend upon our world.[%p]"

msgid "15800:[name]あやせ[line]「復活を阻止するには、グラジオールが流した黒い血によって作られた、七つの杭が必要」[%p]"
msgstr "15800:[name]あやせ[line]Seven stakes, forged from the black blood he shed, are needed to stop his revival.[%p]"

msgid "15900:[name]あやせ[line]「杭は剣へと形を変え、神罰を乗り越えた七人の黒騎士の手に渡る」[%p]"
msgstr "15900:[name]あやせ[line]The stakes will become swords, passed into the hands of seven black knights who have overcome the divine punishment of God.[%p]"

msgid "16000:[name]あやせ[line]「目には目を。歯には歯を」[%p]"
msgstr "16000:[name]あやせ[line]An eye for an eye. A tooth for a tooth.[%p]"

msgid "16100:[name]あやせ[line]「邪心を背負いし人間だけが、邪心王を滅ぼせるのよ」[%p]"
msgstr "16100:[name]あやせ[line]Only humans who bear wicked hearts of their own can defeat the King of Wicked Hearts.[%p]"

msgid "16200:[name]青年刑事[line]「な、なんか映画みたいッスねえ」[%p]"
msgstr "16200:[name]青年刑事[line]I-It's kind of like a movie, huh?[%p]"

msgid "16300:[name]青年刑事[line]「そういう壮大な設定は好きッス！」[%p]"
msgstr "16300:[name]青年刑事[line]I love it when they've got a cool backstory like that![%p]"

msgid "16400:刑事の感想に、あやせは目を細めた。[%p]"
msgstr "16400:Ayase's eyes narrowed at the detective's comment.[%p]"

msgid "16500:[name]あやせ[line]「“設定”じゃないわ」[%p]"
msgstr "16500:[name]あやせ[line]It's not a “story.”[%p]"

msgid "16600:[name]あやせ[line]「現実よ」[%p]"
msgstr "16600:[name]あやせ[line]It's real.[%p]"

msgid "16700:[name]青年刑事[line]「じゃあ、最後の質問ッス」[%p]"
msgstr "16700:[name]青年刑事[line]Okay, last question.[%p]"

msgid "16800:刑事があやせの反論をあっさりと受け流す。[linebreak]だがそういう反応をされることに、彼女は慣れていた。[%p]"
msgstr "16800:The detective ignored her protests, but she was used to that.[%p]"

msgid "16900:あやせの話を信じる者など、これまでにも誰ひとりとしていなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "16900:Nobody had ever believed what she had to say.[%p]"

msgid "17000:[name]青年刑事[line]「キミや西條くんの他にも、翠明の生徒について何人か洗ったんスけどね」[%p]"
msgstr "17000:[name]青年刑事[line]We did some checking on a bunch of Suimei students besides you and Nishijo.[%p]"

msgid "17100:[name]青年刑事[line]「ん〜…………」[%p]"
msgstr "17100:[name]青年刑事[line]Hmmm...[%p]"

msgid "17200:刑事は腕を組んでうなり出す。[%p]"
msgstr "17200:He crossed his arms and heaved a little sigh.[%p]"

msgid "17300:それもまた芝居がかっているが、あやせはそれについてなにか言うつもりはなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "17300:It felt like an obvious act, but Ayase wasn't inclined to call him out.[%p]"

msgid "17400:[name]あやせ[line]「……なに？」[%p]"
msgstr "17400:[name]あやせ[line]What?[%p]"

msgid "17500:[name]青年刑事[line]「そのぉ、すごくバカバカしい質問なんスけど……」[%p]"
msgstr "17500:[name]青年刑事[line]This is a really stupid question.[%p]"

msgid "17600:[name]青年刑事[line]「刑事が質問するようなことじゃないんスよねえ、ホントは……」[%p]"
msgstr "17600:[name]青年刑事[line]And I know it's not the kind of thing a cop's supposed to ask.[%p]"

msgid "17700:[name]青年刑事[line]「子供じみてるって言うか……」[%p]"
msgstr "17700:[name]青年刑事[line]It's kind of... childish.[%p]"

msgid "17800:[name]あやせ[line]「そう……」[%p]"
msgstr "17800:[name]あやせ[line]I see.[%p]"

msgid "17900:[name]あやせ[line]「質問する気がないなら、出て行って」[%p]"
msgstr "17900:[name]あやせ[line]If you're not going to ask the question, then leave.[%p]"

msgid "18000:[name]あやせ[line]「頭が……痛いの」[%p]"
msgstr "18000:[name]あやせ[line]My head... hurts.[%p]"

msgid "18100:[name]青年刑事[line]「ああ、いや、実はね、判さんが妙なこと言い出してるんスよ」[%p]"
msgstr "18100:[name]青年刑事[line]Oh, actually... Ban was saying something weird.[%p]"

msgid "18200:[name]青年刑事[line]「キミたちは魔法使い、なんじゃないかって」[%p]"
msgstr "18200:[name]青年刑事[line]That you guys might be “mages.”[%p]"

msgid "18300:“キミたち”という言葉に、あやせはわずかに眉をひそめた。[%p]"
msgstr "18300:Ayase's eyes narrowed, just a little, at the phrase “you guys.”[%p]"

msgid "18400:[name]青年刑事[line]「違いまスよねえ？」[%p]"
msgstr "18400:[name]青年刑事[line]That's not true, is it?[%p]"

msgid "18500:[name]あやせ[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "18500:[name]あやせ[line]...[%p]"

msgid "18600:[name]あやせ[line]「使えるわ」[%p]"
msgstr "18600:[name]あやせ[line]It's true.[%p]"

msgid "18700:刑事の方は見ず、シーツの上に置いた自身の手を眺めたまま、あやせは答えた。[%p]"
msgstr "18700:She was looking down at her hands instead of at the detective as she spoke.[%p]"

msgid "18800:[name]青年刑事[line]「ははは、あやせちゃんって面白い子ッスね」[%p]"
msgstr "18800:[name]青年刑事[line]Hahaha. You're a fascinating girl, Ayase.[%p]"

msgid "18900:[name]あやせ[line]「でも」[%p]"
msgstr "18900:[name]あやせ[line]But...[%p]"

msgid "19000:[name]あやせ[line]「ニュージェネは、グラジオールの騎士とは無関係」[%p]"
msgstr "19000:[name]あやせ[line]NewGen has nothing to do with Gladiale.[%p]"

msgid "19100:[name]青年刑事[line]「はあ、そうッスか」[%p]"
msgstr "19100:[name]青年刑事[line]I, uh, see.[%p]"

msgid "19200:[name]青年刑事[line]「まあ、どうでもいいんスけどね」[%p]"
msgstr "19200:[name]青年刑事[line]Well, whatever.[%p]"

msgid "19300:刑事はあやせの言葉を興味なさげに受け流し、大きく伸びをした。[%p]"
msgstr "19300:The detective yawned after he spoke, disinterest in his voice.[%p]"

msgid "19400:と、静かだった病室に、唐突に電子音が響き渡った。[linebreak]刑事が慌てた様子で、スーツのポケットからケータイを取り出す。[%p]"
msgstr "19400:And then, suddenly, an electronic sound filled the room. The detective frantically pulled a phone out of his suit pocket.[%p]"

msgid "19500:[name]青年刑事[line]「まずったぁ、病院ってケータイ禁止なんスよね。電源ＯＦＦにしておくの、忘れてた」[%p]"
msgstr "19500:[name]青年刑事[line]Crap. You're not supposed to use your phone in a hospital. I forgot to turn it off.[%p]"

msgid "19600:[name]青年刑事[line]「うわ、しかも女からだし」[%p]"
msgstr "19600:[name]青年刑事[line]Uwah... And it's from a girl, too.[%p]"

msgid "19700:[name]青年刑事[line]「へへ、付き合って４年になるラブラブのカノジョがいるんスよ〜」[%p]"
msgstr "19700:[name]青年刑事[line]Heheh. I've got a girl I'm in love with. We've been dating for four years.[%p]"

msgid "19800:ニヤけながら通話ＯＦＦボタンを押して、相手からの着信を強制的に切ってしまった。[linebreak]それから、改めてあやせに向き直ってくる。[%p]"
msgstr "19800:He grinned as he pressed the button to reject the call. He turned back toward Ayase.[%p]"

msgid "19900:[name]青年刑事[line]「あやせちゃんは映画見るッスか？」[%p]"
msgstr "19900:[name]青年刑事[line]You a movie buff, Ayase?[%p]"

msgid "20000:[name]青年刑事[line]「『スパークウォーズ』って知らない？\u3000それに出てくるダーススパイダー伯爵のテーマなんス、今のメロディ」[%p]"
msgstr "20000:[name]青年刑事[line]You ever heard of Spark Wars? That was Count Darth Spider's theme. He's a character in the movie.[%p]"

msgid "20100:彼女は映画になど興味はなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "20100:She wasn't interested in movies at all.[%p]"

msgid "20200:もうすでに、この刑事の質問に答える義務も必要性もないと判断し、黙って窓の外へと視線を移す。[%p]"
msgstr "20200:Ayase had already decided she was under no obligation to answer any more of his questions, and silently turned to look out the window.[%p]"

msgid "20300:[name]青年刑事[line]「実は自分、『スパークウォーズ』オタクなんスよ〜」[%p]"
msgstr "20300:[name]青年刑事[line]I'm a huge Spark Wars geek, you know.[%p]"

msgid "20400:[name]青年刑事[line]「あ、興味ないッスか。そりゃ失礼したッス」[%p]"
msgstr "20400:[name]青年刑事[line]Oh, you don't care? Sorry, then.[%p]"

msgid "20500:[name]青年刑事[line]「んじゃ、自分はこれで」[%p]"
msgstr "20500:[name]青年刑事[line]Anyway, have a nice night.[%p]"

msgid "20600:最後は一方的に話して、刑事は病室を出ていった。[%p]"
msgstr "20600:The detective left the room without waiting for her answer.[%p]"

msgid "20700:あやせの目はその後ろ姿を見送ろうともせず。[%p]"
msgstr "20700:Ayase didn't bother to watch him as he went.[%p]"

msgid "20800:黄昏色から藍色へと変わりつつある空だけを映していた。[%p]"
msgstr "20800:Her eyes were watching the sky as it shifted from twilight to azure night.[%p]"

